1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:57:18.000Z","msg":"懶人包：<br />\n柴灣地鐵站0050左右有full gear 狗入內截查站內接放學既手足。消息指徐子見被捕。另外站內其它接放學手足相信同樣被捕。<br />\n<br />\n事件起因：<br />\n今晚較早時，有熱心人喺柴灣站等候接放學<br />\n頭先地鐵停駛後，仍然有熱心人留守等緊翻黎既手足<br />\n有乘客因為不滿意港鐵突然停駛而去客務中心同職員理論，維持左1+ hour<br />\n有理由相信職員因此報驚。"},{"pid":"d46e2a96c411907fc6da6034d5f8ec9f3800d344","tid":1524502,"uid":169207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:57:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mSpP8pQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmSpP8pQ.jpg&h=9426be84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wUD5GKS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwUD5GKS.jpg&h=5fe937c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KVvWOpU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKVvWOpU.jpg&h=ea761e81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BKfDhih.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBKfDhih.jpg&h=3f2dc27c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A0xaSRE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA0xaSRE.jpg&h=529769b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iQzkvDm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiQzkvDm.jpg&h=2d664012&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f8b770e9cc5f5131819d4ff30fc07a865a9ea35","tid":1524502,"uid":227981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d37017676077396d7859bf8295bdc0bb9b2cb02b","tid":1524502,"uid":123991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:23:57.000Z","msg":"我知大家好撚嬲, 因為我地冇清算黨鐵先搞到今日咁, 但係要記得今日要去春袋報仇, 黨鐵黎緊一齊再清算！香港人加油 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dyrx7H5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyrx7H5.gif&h=f7c0f28c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwi